  "title": "Automation Engineer",
  "description": "<p>If you are enthusiastic, driven, creative and result orientated, we welcome you to join our company and be part of our team. SYE is an equal opportunity employer, offering a great work environment and challenging career opportunities.</p>\n<p><strong>PLC and HMI/SCADA Programming</strong></p>\n<p>Your responsibilities will mainly be PLC and SCADA Programming. No experience is required. We welcome applications from local polytechnics (Engineering, Computer Science or related field) or just out of National Service. If you have a desire to learn industrial automation processes, we will provide the necessary tools and training for you.</p>\n<p>You will be involved in all phases of project implementation, from design, to engineering, implementation, testing and commissioning. You will coordinate with other members of the project team, customers and contractors on engineering and project activites to ensure that the project is executed in a timely and cost effective manner.</p>\n<p>Salary will be commensurate with relevant experience and education.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>",
