    "description": "<p>We are an automation integrator based in Singapore and focused on the Asian region.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We provide solutions for process automation for Waste Incineration Plants, Oil and Gas Industry, Water Treatment Plants, Power Plants.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Our engineers have extensive experience in design, programming and project implementation, from compressor systems, simple start/stop automation, simple sequences, to plant wide monitoring systems with loop control, alarms, and extensive reporting.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>We welcome you to find out more about us, and can be contacted via email at info@shenyi.com.sg or by phone at 6320 9133 / 6320 9137.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><br></p>",
